<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Certificate of Completion</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #e0f7fa; /* Light aqua background */
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .certificate {
            position: relative;
            border: 5px solid #4CAF50; /* Green border */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px; /* Rounded corners */
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px; /* Maximum width for certificate */
            overflow: hidden; /* Hide overflow for patterns */
        }

        .certificate::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            left: -30px;
            right: -30px;
            bottom: -30px;
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/paper.png'); /* Background pattern */
            opacity: 0.2; /* Make it subtle */
            z-index: 0; /* Behind the content */
            border-radius: 15px; /* Match border radius */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50; /* Title color */
            margin-top: 0; /* Remove margin */
            font-size: 2.5em; /* Increase font size */
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it stays above background */
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3f51b5; /* Darker color for name */
            font-size: 2em; /* Increase font size */
            margin: 10px 0; /* Add some margin */
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it stays above background */
        }

        h3 {
            color: #2196f3; /* Blue color for course */
            font-size: 1.5em; /* Increase font size */
            margin: 10px 0; /* Add some margin */
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it stays above background */
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 50px;
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it stays above background */
        }

        .signature img {
            width: 100px; /* Set width for signature image */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
        }

        .signature p {
            margin: 5px 0; /* Add some margin */
            font-style: italic; /* Italicize signature */
        }

        p {
            color: #555; /* Dark gray color for text */
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Slightly larger font for readability */
            margin: 10px 0; /* Add some margin */
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it stays above background */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="certificate">
        <h1>Certificate of Completion</h1>
        <p>This certifies that</p>
        <h2><%= fname %> <%= lname %> ü•á</h2>
        <p>has successfully completed the ‚úç</p>
        <h3>Web Development üíª in CodeArt Academy</h3>
        <p>on this day, <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>